name: Strength In Numbers (NEAAP)
description: Thanks for coming here!  To play use WASD to move around. Press E to use a stomp attack ideal for close targets.  Press Q to grab a rock, move the mouse around to aim, and left click to throw it.  The goal? Get to the castle and destroy it to win.  Try not to get subdued by the many little archers, and guards.   Any feedback (especially towards the 3rd person rock attack) is appreciated.  I did have to submit this early as I have school tomorrow.  I hope you have fun!
